        settings.  From Sebastien Lorquet.

    * STMicro STM32 Boards:

      - STM32F103 Minimum: Fix Timers 2 to 7 clock frequencies. From Alan
        Carvalho de Assis.
      - Nucleo-F303RE:  Remove duplicate setting from board.h.   From  Marc
        Recht.
