      - STM32L476-MDK:  Add support for the on-board LEDs.
      - Nucleo-L496ZG:  Add DFSDM initialization.  From Juha Niskanen
      - Nucleo-L496ZG:  Add support for SDMMC driver.  From Miha Vrhovnik.
